I‚Äôve downloaded the Talon Fx Swerve Template and incorporated the Vision template and the drive base works fine. Unfortunately our autonomous routines are inconsistent and both the wheel radius characterization and feedforward characterization tests are not working. The wheel radius test jerks the wheels and returns a value but the robot never rotates. The feedforward test does not lead to any actions from the robot. I have not performed the slip current or max speed tests yet.
We run 2 ov9281‚Äôs connected to an orange pi 5 and are also struggling to update our pose from from the vision measurements.
I have already tuned in the P.I.D. values to our robot and we drive smoothly but I want to figure out both the characterization test issues and vision issues to improve our robot for the district championship and next season.
Thanks for the help in advance and I‚Äôve attached a link to our code here.
